plot: Kite and company arrive at NGL's drug factory and run into Yunju's team, where a fight begins. Meanwhile, Rammot is introduced to Nen.

Searching for the Chimera Ant's nest, Kite and the boys confirm their suspicions about the NGL and must face three dangerous enemies in order to proceed. Meanwhile, Rammot wants to payback Gon and Killua for his defeat and ends up unwittingly unlocking the power of Nen in his body.—paulp1988
